## Database Tables

- `users` — email, password_hash, name, is_admin, is_subscribed, language
- `content` — title (ar+en), description (ar+en), hls_url, hls_variants (JSONB), tags, languages, region_tags, subtitles, is_premium, network_quality_hint, duration, type
- `stream_tokens` — temp tokens for content playback
- `analytics_events` — playback event tracking
- `payments` — mock payment records

## Key API Routes

- `POST /api/auth/register` — register
- `POST /api/auth/login` — login → returns JWT
- `GET/PUT /api/auth/profile` — user profile + language pref
- `GET /api/content` — list (supports ?q=, ?lang=, ?region=, ?page=, ?limit=)
- `GET /api/content/:id` — detail
- `POST/PUT/DELETE /api/content/:id` — admin CRUD
- `POST /api/stream-token` — get HLS playback URL (checks subscription for premium)
- `POST /api/payments` — mock subscription payment
- `POST /api/analytics/events` — record playback event
- `GET /api/analytics` — admin analytics view

## Frontend Pages

- `/` — Home/Library with hero + content grid
- `/content/:id` — Content detail with Play button
- `/player/:id` — HLS player with controls
- `/login`, `/register` — Auth pages
- `/profile` — Language preference, subscription status
- `/admin` — Admin content list (admin only)
- `/admin/content/new`, `/admin/content/:id/edit` — Content editor
- `/admin/analytics` — Analytics table
- `/network-test` — Network simulation page
- `/search` — Search results

